title: Keto Bread
directions: In a food processor, pulse almond flour, egg white protein, cream of tartar, baking soda, and salt
Transfer batter into a greased 9 x 5 inch baking dish
Bake at 350°F for 45-50 minutes, or until a toothpick stuck in the center comes out clean
Cool for 2 hours, then remove from pan
ingredients: 2 tablespoonsegg white protein powder or organic egg white protein powder
